Inzvi iri rinoreva zvinhu zviviri. Chekutanga, ''dandira'' chirukwa chinoitwa ne[[zvipembenene]] zvinonzi ma[[dandemutande]]. Chepiri, ''dandira'' nderumwe rudzi gwechimera chinogona kuwawanikwa mumunda sebundo chinokura chotandira pasi pazvimbo yakakura kana kumonera pahunde yomuti chotevedza matavi ese emuti uyu. Mazuva ano, inzvi rokuti ''dandira'' tinogona kuritora torishandisa mukureva chinonzi "web" mu[[Chirungu]].
